LIVE DB VIEW

These files are readable exports of the current FoodNest Oracle tables.
They are for viewing inside the FoodNest project folder.

MAIN TABLES
- users.table
- user_profiles.table
- user_sessions.table
- menu_items.table
- orders.table
- order_items.table
- delivery_assignments.table
- order_status_history.table
- feedback.table

ROLE DATA LOCATION
- Hosteller accounts: users.table + user_profiles.table
- Home cook accounts: users.table + user_profiles.table + menu_items.table
- Delivery agent accounts: users.table + user_profiles.table + delivery_assignments.table
- Orders: orders.table + order_items.table + order_status_history.table
- Ratings and reviews: feedback.table
